* {{citation |last=Hobson |first=Benjamin |display-authors=0 |title=''《惠爱醫館年記》 [''Huìài Yīguǎn Niánjì'' or ''Hwuy Gae E Kwan Nëen Ke, Annual Report of the Missionary Hospital at Canton'']'' |location=Guangzhou |date=1850 }}. {{zh icon}}
* {{citation |last=Hobson |first=Benjamin |display-authors=0 |title=''《全體新論》 [''Quántǐ Xīnlún'' or ''Tseuen T'e Sin Lun, Treatise on Physiology'']'' |location=Guangzhou |date=1851 }}.{{refn|group=n|Also translated as ''A New Theory of the Body''.<ref name=taiduo/>}} {{zh icon}}
* {{citation |last=Hobson |first=Benjamin |display-authors=0 |title=''《上帝辨證》 [''Shàngdì Biànzhèng'' or ''Shang Te Pëen Ching, Theological Evidences'']'' |location=Guangzhou |date=1852 }}. {{zh icon}}
* {{citation |last=Hobson |first=Benjamin |display-authors=0 |title=''《約翰真經释解》 [''Yuēhàn Zhēnjīng Shìxiè'' or ''Yo Han Chin King Shih Keae, Commentary on John's Gospel'']'' |location=Hong Kong |date=1853 }}. {{zh icon}}
* {{citation |last=Hobson |first=Benjamin |display-authors=0 |title=''《祈祷式文》 [''Qídǎo Shìwén'' or ''K'e Taou Shih Wan, Forms of Prayer'']'' |location=Guangzhou |date=1854 }}, revised ed. 1865. {{zh icon}}
* {{citation |last=Hobson |first=Benjamin |display-authors=0 |title=''《問答良言》 [''Wèndá Liángyán'' or ''Wan Ta Lëang Yen, Catechism of Christian Principles'']'' |location=Guangzhou |date=1855 }}, reprinted at Shanghai 1857. {{zh icon}}
* {{citation |last=Hobson |first=Benjamin |display-authors=0 |title=''《信德之解》 [''Xìndé zhī Xiè'' or ''Sin Tih Che Keae, Explanation of Faith'']'' |location=Guangzhou |date=1855 }}. {{zh icon}}
* {{citation |last=Hobson |first=Benjamin |display-authors=0 |title=''《博物新編》 [''Bówù Xīnbiān'' or ''Po Wuh Sin Pëen, Natural Philosophy'']'' |location=Guangzhou |date=1855 }}. {{zh icon}}
